	<description>
		<p>ABOUT 4KTUBE :</p>
		<p>4KTUBE is a fast, powerful, and user-friendly application designed to download YouTube videos, playlists, and music in high-definition (HD, 4K, 8K) effortlessly.</p>
		<p>WHY CHOOSE 4KTUBE?</p>
			<ul>
				<li>One-click YouTube video and audio downloader: Save videos in MP4, WEBM, MP3, and more formats instantly.</li>
				<li>Download full YouTube playlists: Save entire playlists with a single click.</li>
				<li>YouTube multi-language audio support: Download videos with multiple dubbed audio tracks.</li>
				<li>YouTube subtitles and closed captions download: Extract videos with embedded subtitles.</li>
				<li>Sign-in-required videos: Now you can download sign-in-required videos from YouTube by authenticating your account.</li>
				<li>Batch downloading: Save multiple videos simultaneously for faster downloads.</li>
				<li>YouTube music and audio extractor: Convert YouTube videos into high-quality MP3 files.</li>
				<li>Multi-platform video downloader: Download from Facebook, Instagram, TikTok, Twitter, Twitch, Vimeo, Rumble, Odysee, Bitchute, Reddit, SoundCloud, and 1400+ other platforms.</li>
				<li>Ad-free YouTube streaming: Play videos without annoying ads.</li>
				<li>Super-fast download speeds: Optimized for high-speed, high-quality downloads.</li>
				<li>Search YouTube directly in the app: Find and download videos quickly with regional language support.</li>
				<li>Lightweight, secure and private: No ads, no trackers, no malware – just seamless downloads.</li>
    		</ul>
		 <p>WHAT SETS 4KTUBE APART?</p>
			<ul>
			  <li>Supports 4K and 8K Ultra HD video downloads</li>
			  <li>Optimized for the fastest download speeds</li>
			  <li>Easily Authenticate YouTube account for sign-in-required videos</li>
			  <li>User-friendly, minimalist interface</li>
			  <li>Regular updates with new platform support</li>
			</ul>
		 <p>LANGUAGE SUPPORT :</p>
		<ul>
			<li>4KTUBE is available in 35+ popular international languages, including German, French, Spanish, Italian, Dutch, Portuguese, Japanese, Polish, Swedish, Chinese, Russian and more.</li>
		</ul>
	</description>
